99
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:20,430
I'll bet this has something to do with
that Digimon gen I was talking about.

100
00:04:20,431 --> 00:04:22,890
Either that or it's a giant cube puzzle.

101
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:38,380
I am the ultimate evil, complete with hot
and cold running water.

102
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,320
What on earth is that thing?

103
00:04:40,321 --> 00:04:43,140
I am Apokalomon, a mutant Digimon.

104
00:04:43,420 --> 00:04:46,480
My darkness zone attack transforms my
enemy into nothingness.

105
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:49,700
I have the power to turn everything I
touch into total darkness.

106
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,840
