challenge and simply disappeared.

120
00:05:29,020 --> 00:05:30,020
That makes sense.

121
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:33,260
Even on earth, some species became extinct
during the process of evolution.

122
00:05:33,261 --> 00:05:37,081
In fact, the Tasmanian tiger
wolf was one of those... Silence!

123
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,280
Who's the one telling this story anyway?

124
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,060
Me or you?

125
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,400
Alright, go ahead.

126
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,080
First, I have a question to ask.

127
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,900
Do you believe that I am worthy of
coexisting with you?

128
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:50,040
Uh, well... yeah, sure.

129
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,520
Oh, really?

130
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:54,835
Even though I was forged from
the pain and misery of all the

131
