174
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:45,280
He's using all the attacks of the evil
Digimon we've defeated in the past!

175
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:47,280
You mean we have to fight them all over
again?

176
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:49,900
This is the worst recurring nightmare I've
ever been awake for!

177
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,320
Hey, we were able to beat them once!

178
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:53,300
Sora's right!

179
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:54,560
We did beat them!

180
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:55,840
And we can do it again!

181
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,220
We just have to fight together as a team!

182
00:07:59,080 --> 00:07:59,860
